original_title: TNA Best of the X Division Vol. 2
overview: The no-limits stars of TNA's X Division continue to revolutionize the sport of professional wrestling. With moves never before witnessed inside a ring, these daredevils are among the most exciting athletes in all of sports. On this DVD, you'll witness the best of X Division stars such as Samoa Joe, A.J. Styles, Christopher Daniels, Chris Sabin, Petey Williams, and many more in some of the most action-packed bouts in TNA Wrestling history.
title: TNA Best of the X Division Vol. 2
